{"tid":1809832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【燉】撐警奀星誓死效忠恐怖份子：「就算做乞丐也唔會妥協」","createTime":"2020-01-03T11:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T14:12:31.000Z","uid":202464,"like":304,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5cd514e9b9096e6378bb0839e5a527b5db325a","tid":1809832,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H6JrMqH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH6JrMqH.jpg&h=8a3c5990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n撐警奀星去年12月到恐怖份子基地送暖，在支那社交網站貼出與雙花紅棍江xx、白紙扇郭YY及謝ZZ等合照，並留言表示：「正能量香港黑社會不離不棄。」<br />\n<br />\n結果在元旦日，灣仔店「燉」被打爆玻璃，有藍屍看到後私下傳訊息慰問，不過撐警奀星就好霸氣地表示頂得住，更指：<br />\n<br />\n「生意沒了隨時可以再做，人性沒了不知道怎樣找回來，就算我做乞丐也唔會妥協，永遠支持香港黑社會。」<br />\n<br />\n一眾支那網民均大讚撐警奀星是「真漢子」，更表示歡迎他到大灣區開店。"},{"pid":"2183961c234482eddfa976832ce9921228e16647","tid":1809832,"uid":205339,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"已經你已經係"},{"pid":"dd6c2e746d53a32e4cf2ba1449102a43856d4cbe","tid":1809832,"uid":107681,"like":111,"dislike":0,"score":111,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"去武漢開鋪，肺炎燉野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb52d3529d0716cbb874186f1923d827b80ed042","tid":1809832,"uid":76776,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:13:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67603bf7891d66f794206b27fb5a48b3cf1af9f3","tid":1809832,"uid":38904,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"本身已經冇生意, 人性同做緊乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa75cc0eb3f75de824d3549ca54941ec3c2f0ba","tid":1809832,"uid":288048,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:14:21.000Z","msg":"邊位"},{"pid":"46ced754c40558fc3f9b64529ad40c82bb2ca686","tid":1809832,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"Push